summary:
Hi! I'm Vafa

I have a pleasant approach, strong interpersonal and problem solving skills, with humor I easily connect to people and maintain a cheerful, playful spirit to the team. I try to combine my hobbies such as reading, cooking, photography and video making to deliver an easy accessible and eye catching product.
